                <h1>Nearly 6 months after HRL said safety review would be &#039;finished shortly,&#039; 300 Swift balconies still closed</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/f0b5948b-463f-46b9-9671-e5a17cafddec.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

